org.anchoranalysis.image.core.channel.convert

Class ToUnsignedByte

  • Object
    • ChannelConverter<UnsignedByteBuffer>
      • ToUnsignedByte

  • public class ToUnsignedByte
extends ChannelConverter<UnsignedByteBuffer>
    Converts from other data types to UnsignedByteBuffer (unsigned 8-bit) without scaling.

    This implies undefined behaviour for values in the source data-type that lie outside the range of UnsignedByteBuffer.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
